@startuml chat_sequence
actor User
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "API Server" as API
participant "Retrieval\nMiddleware" as MW
participant "Vector Store" as VS
participant "Intent\nExtractor" as IE
participant "Exercise\nDatabase" as EDB
participant "LLM Agent" as LLM

User -> FE : Send message
FE -> API : POST /chat (message + history)
API -> MW : Intercept request
MW -> VS : Similarity search (K=2)
VS --> MW : Relevant chunks
MW -> LLM : Augmented prompt\n(system prompt + retrieved context)

alt Workout request
    LLM -> IE : Extract structured intent
    IE --> LLM : {muscle, equipment,\ndifficulty, count}
    LLM -> EDB : Filter exercises
    EDB --> LLM : Matching exercises (unordered)
end

LLM --> API : Generated response\n(exercises ordered by training rules)
API --> FE : JSON response
FE --> User : Display answer
@enduml
